`,s.jsxs(c.p,{children:["In early 2022, I connected with ",s.jsx(c.a,{href:"https://dellmed.utexas.edu/directory/gregory-greg-fonzo",children:"Dr. Greg Fonzo"})," shortly after hearing about the recent opening of UT's ",s.jsx(c.em,{children:"Center for Psychedelic Research & Therapy"}),". ",s.jsx(c.strong,{children:"Psychedelic assisted therapy"})," is something I believe in and I wanted to find out how I could help."]}),`
